<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٧٠٣٩ - عَنْ عَبْدِ الْقُدُّوسِ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ نَافِعٍ قَالَ:</span> وَجَدَ عُمَرُ فِي بَيْتِ رُوَيْشِدٍ الثَّقَفِيِّ،<span class="c5"> خَمْرًا فَحَرَّقَ بَيْتَهُ وَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَا اسْمُكَ؟»</span> قَالَ: رُوَيْشِدٌ قَالَ: <span class="c2">«بَلْ أَنْتَ فُوَيْسِقٌ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>